data.description: ~Welcome Home to all that the desirable Waterfall Community has to offer. Single story 3 bedroom 2 bath home with a pool and loaded with extras in gated community. The large living room welcomes you to the open floor plan. Spacious kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, built in beverage cooler, pantry & tasteful back-splash. House has a central vacuuming system installed, separate large family room, master bedroom is separate from secondary bedrooms. Upgraded flooring, ceiling fans and shades in most rooms. Hot Water heater installed 2022, Water Softener included and paid off. Refreshing heated pool with jets retractable awning installed in backyard. Grass is low maintenance synthetic grass. SOLAR system is owned and paid off. Numerous walking parks, playgrounds & green areas against a backdrop of the Shepard Mountains. Large Clubhouse with attached community pool and separate spa plus exercise room, meeting room & much more!
